たぶん、jest でいう each みたいなのが欲しいんですよね?
<https://jestjs.io/docs/en/api#testeachtablename-fn-timeout>
```test.each`
  a    | b    | expected
  ${1} | ${1} | ${2}
  ${1} | ${2} | ${3}
  ${2} | ${1} | ${3}
`('returns $expected when $a is added $b', ({a, b, expected}) =&gt; {
  expect(a + b).toBe(expected);
});```
